        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-08-16 15:34:54.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nDoes transparent really need to be indexed?\nWhat is the purpose for adding prov-status,networkRef,transparent and operational-status to searchable? I don't think this does what you think.",
        "patchset_number": 3
      },
      {
        "id": "1846ccb56d2744e1bd3382751b2148a4bd8a2a80",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 4341,
          "name": "Keong Lim",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "keong.lim+onap@gmail.com",
          "username": "keong"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2018-08-16 16:11:44.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nHi Christina,\nWhat is the exact purpose of the \"searchable\" property?\nHow can I observe the difference between adding or removing attributes from the \"searchable\" property?\n\nI will ask the developers about having transparent be indexed.\nThanks",
        "patchset_number": 3
      },
      {
        "id": "d8cef805eaea8cb621eca1f471118784be4c8ebe",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 3405,
          "name": "Christina Monteleone",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "christina.monteleone@att.com",
          "username": "CMonteleone"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-08-16 16:52:26.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nProperties do not need to be added to searchable in order to use them as query parameters. You can still do .../p-interfaces?network-ref={value} without it. Searchable is related to the A&AI UI microservices.",
        "patchset_number": 3
      },
